data.description: Looking for the perfect starter home in the heart of Las Vegas? Then look no further! This adorable home is located in the heart of Spring Valley, just minutes away from all of the shopping available at Rainbow and the 215 and just a seven-minute drive to Allegiant Stadium and the strip, talk about location! This lovely community is gated and also has a community pool and spa, perfect for cooling off on those hot summer days with none of the maintenance! Once you drive up to this charming home, you'll find a welcoming living room, quaint kitchen, two bedrooms, two baths, and an appealing backyard, perfect to relax in and relatively maintenance free. Don't miss out on the chance to make this charming property your home!
